      "question_zh": "考虑氨基酸异亮氨酸的结构,其结构式如下:\n\n\\begin{center}\n\\chemfig{\n    \\chemsetup{atom sep=2em}\n    \\chemsetup{\n        \\definesubmol{isoleucine}{\n            (-[:90](-[:-30]\\Lewis{7,9}N)(-[#6](-[:-90]%\n                \\Lewis{6,7}\\phantom{H}\\phantom{H}%\n                \\Lewis{5,6}\\phantom{H}\\phantom{H}%\n                \\Lewis{4,5}\\phantom{H}\\phantom{H}%\n                \\Lewis{3,4}\\phantom{H}\\phantom{H}%\n                \\Lewis{2,3}\\phantom{H}\\phantom{H}%\n                \\Lewis{1,2}\\phantom{H}\\phantom{H}%\n                \\Lewis{0,1}\\phantom{H}%\n            )(-[:-30]\\Lewis{8,9}O)(-[#6](-[:-150]%\n                \\Lewis{14,15}\\phantom{H}\\phantom{H}%\n                \\Lewis{13,14}\\phantom{H}\\phantom{H}%\n                \\Lewis{12,13}\\phantom{H}\\phantom{H}%\n            )(-[:-90]\\Lewis{11,12}C)(-[:-30]\\Lewis{10,11}H))\n        }\n    }\n    \\chemfig{*6(--\\isoleucine)}\n\\end{center}\n\n异亮氨酸分子中存在两个手性碳原子,因此共有四种光学异构体。",
